---
title: Sweet & Spicy Thai Steak Salad  with Crispy Rice, Charred Scallions & Toasted Peanuts
description: Get ready for a tastebud takeover with this Thai-inspired salad! You’ll sizzle tender bavette steaks to juicy perfection, then slice and serve on a bed of mixed greens, crispy fried rice, charred scallions, and juicy tomatoes in a sweet-spicy-tangy dressing. Garnish with toasted peanuts for a crunchy finish.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66f2dbb988e18f7212d3fc30-ebce0dd4.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/66f2dbb988e18f7212d3fc30-en-US.pdf
